Quran 15:87 وَلَقَدْ ءَاتَيْنَٰكَ سَبْعًۭا مِّنَ ٱلْمَثَانِى وَٱلْقُرْءَانَ ٱلْعَظِيمَ "We have given you seven of the doubly-recited verses (Key) and the Grand Quran (Message)."
Book = Key + Message Key = الفاتحة = The Opener (not the opening) Chapters 114 = 1 + 113 additive prime numbers Verses 6236 = 7 + 6229 additive prime numbers
Key = 7 verses = 29 words = 139 letters additive prime numbers
Primalogy value of The Key = 8317 additive prime numbers Primalogy values of all verses of The Key additive composite numbers
Quran 89:3 وَٱلشَّفْعِ وَٱلْوَتْرِ "I swear by the Co-dependent (composite numbers) and by the Independent (prime numbers)"
Quran 72:28 لِّيَعْلَمَ أَن قَدْ أَبْلَغُوا۟ رِسَٰلَٰتِ رَبِّهِمْ وَأَحَاطَ بِمَا لَدَيْهِمْ وَأَحْصَىٰ كُلَّ شَىْءٍ عَدَدًۢا " ... and He accounted all things in numbers."
Prime numbers are God's Signature!
